Type: ShinyApp
Title: MarineSABRES SES Toolbox
Version: 1.11.0
Description: R/Shiny application for Social-Ecological Systems (SES) analysis
    using the DAPSIWRM framework. Supports 9 languages with reactive i18n,
    network visualization, and ML-assisted element classification.
